dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Paso Robles quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by contours.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle PASO ROBLES, CA 1948, DMA 1855 II NW -- Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1979."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
